  <!-- ════════ THE HONESTY BACKTEST ════════ -->
  <section class="dp-section" id="backtest">
    <div class="dp-eyebrow">The test any &ldquo;cheap or expensive&rdquo; claim should pass</div>
    <h2 class="dp-h2">What this lens said at past extremes</h2>
    <p class="dp-lead">Every figure below is computed by the same code that drives the slider above, run against the market&rsquo;s four cyclical tops. The same arithmetic that reads high today read <strong>deeply negative at every major top</strong>. That is what an instrument, rather than a pitch, looks like.</p>

    <div class="dp-table-wrap" data-chart-copy data-chart-heading="#backtest .dp-h2" data-chart-sub="#backtest .dp-lead" data-chart-title="What reverting to trend implied at bitcoin's cyclical tops" data-chart-filename="bitcoin-reversion-cagr-backtest.png">
