    <p class="dp-table-note">Implied CAGR of a return to trend from each moment, at one-, two- and three-year horizons. Top anchors are the site&rsquo;s canonical cyclical-top set, shared with <a href="/bitcoin-vs-the-stock-market">Bitcoin vs. The Stock Market</a>; multiples and rates are computed from the model, not asserted.</p>
